        {
            "id": 6011382,
            "title": "前小摩策略師警告：川馬衝突恐觸發美股5-10%修正",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>據《商業內幕》周五 (6 日) 報導，前摩根大通 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:JPM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/JPM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">JPM-US</a>) 首席市場策略師科拉諾維奇 (Marko Kolanovic) 預測美股將修正 5-10%，川普與馬斯克衝突可能成為觸發因素。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011382%2Fl%2F29ce2ddffccc0449eed3d7bfdce17910.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011382%2Fl%2F29ce2ddffccc0449eed3d7bfdce17910.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011382%2Fl%2F29ce2ddffccc0449eed3d7bfdce17910.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011382%2Fl%2F29ce2ddffccc0449eed3d7bfdce17910.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011382%2Fl%2F29ce2ddffccc0449eed3d7bfdce17910.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011382%2Fl%2F29ce2ddffccc0449eed3d7bfdce17910.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011382%2Fl%2F29ce2ddffccc0449eed3d7bfdce17910.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011382%2Fl%2F29ce2ddffccc0449eed3d7bfdce17910.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011382%2Fl%2F29ce2ddffccc0449eed3d7bfdce17910.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011382%2Fl%2F29ce2ddffccc0449eed3d7bfdce17910.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011382%2Fl%2F29ce2ddffccc0449eed3d7bfdce17910.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011382%2Fl%2F29ce2ddffccc0449eed3d7bfdce17910.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011382%2Fl%2F29ce2ddffccc0449eed3d7bfdce17910.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011382%2Fl%2F29ce2ddffccc0449eed3d7bfdce17910.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011382%2Fl%2F29ce2ddffccc0449eed3d7bfdce17910.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011382%2Fl%2F29ce2ddffccc0449eed3d7bfdce17910.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011382%2Fl%2F29ce2ddffccc0449eed3d7bfdce17910.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">特斯拉股價周四重挫14%，小摩前策略師擔心散戶重倉股下跌恐引發連鎖效應。(圖:Shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>科拉諾維奇周四在 CNBC 節目中分析，特斯拉 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSLA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSLA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSLA-US</a>) 是散戶投資人最大持股，其股價下跌可能觸發更大規模的市場回檔。他在 X 平台點名特斯拉、Palantir(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:PLTR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/PLTR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">PLTR-US</a>) 和超微電腦 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SMCI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SMCI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SMCI-US</a>) 等熱門散戶股票可能引發連鎖下跌。特斯拉股價周四因川普與馬斯克衝突重挫 14%。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>他指出，川馬衝突只是眾多風險因素之一，美股目前面臨多重挑戰，包括貿易戰威脅、經濟放緩跡象，以及估值過高等問題。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>科拉諾維奇認為，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">那斯達克</a>指數雖然接近歷史高點，但在利率維持高檔的環境下，股票投資的吸引力下降。目前 10 年期美國公債殖利率徘徊在 4.4% 左右，股票相對於債券的超額報酬率並不理想。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>此外，川普持續施壓聯準會 (Fed) 主席鮑爾降息，也讓市場對聯準會獨立性產生擔憂。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>總體經濟風險也在增加。科拉諾維奇指出，本周稍早公布的 ADP 就業報告疲弱，新增就業僅 3.7 萬人，遠低於經濟學家預期的 11 萬人。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>不過周五公布的 5 月非農報告顯示，就業成長高於預期，但 4 月和 3 月的數據都大幅下修，成為市場隱憂。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>科拉諾維奇表示，修正可能帶來潛在的買進機會，但前提是經濟衰退風險消散。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>過去有「半神」美譽的科拉諾維奇去年 7 月離開摩根大通，結束 19 年職業生涯，原因是連續兩年的市場預測失準。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>他在 2022 年股市大跌 19% 時堅持看多，卻在市場觸底時轉為看空，錯過了 2023 年<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">標普 500 指數</a> 24% 的漲幅以及今年上半年 14% 的漲勢。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6011382",
